summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of the West 20' of Lots 9, 10, 11 and 12, and the south 20' of said Lot 12, Block 94, Lakewood Addition, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-402 and 17-296, respectively.
